            <div class="testimonial-author">
                <img src="/images/testimonials/alex.jpg" alt="Alex K.">
                Alex K.
            </div>
            <p class="testimonial-text">"The laptops align perfectly with my work needs sold by a brand I can trust! I discovered amazing performance..."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="testimonial-rating">★★★★★</div>
            <div class="testimonial-author">
                <img src="/images/testimonials/james.jpg" alt="James L.">
                James L.
            </div>
            <p class="testimonial-text">"A company which is always on the lookout for unique tech products. I'm thrilled to have found this store..."</p>
        </div>
